data.label: zlib
data.description: zlib 设计为一个免费、通用、合法无拘束——即不受任何专利覆盖——的无损数据压缩库，几乎可以在任何计算机硬件和操作系统上使用。

data.label: zlib
data.description: zlib is designed to be a free, general-purpose, legally unencumbered -- that is, not covered by any patents -- lossless data-compression library for use on virtually any computer hardware and operating system.
